(67789, '9EDABF07-2CE5-4A7B-B345-9973CD8FEFFE', 'Hello to my fellow ezra Klein junkies. Next Sunday night, March 26, Zvika and I are hosting an intimate in-person conversation with my Ezra Klein (https://www.nytimes.com/by/ezra-klein) about the simple yet radical notion of the Sabbath. As Ezra explored this topic on a recent episode of his New York Times podcast (https://www.nytimes.com/2023/01/03/opinion/ezra-klein-podcast-judith-shulevitz.html), this ancient practice is more than just a respite from work and technology: it invites an entirely different conception of time, morality, rest and community.   In this discussion, we’ll tackle how we can build our own modern versions of this practice that helps us bring intentionality to the speed at which we live our lives, the ways we choose to spend our time and h ow we think about the idea of rest itself. Please register here. You are welcome to invite friends. https://chochmat.org/events/shabbat-and-the-art-of-rest-a-discussion-with-ezra-klein/?occurrence=2023-03-26 .', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2023-03-16T13:02:38.826840'),
